    "golfOverlay": {
        "h3": "Golf",
        "p": "Here at La Luna Golf Society we play every Wednesday, and all HCPs are welcome. \n\nWe are a group of Norwegians who enjoy ourselves with a good game of golf and build a social network together at the same time. When we have finished playing, head up to La Luna for dinner, and everyone is welcome to bring an extra guest to dinner with them. \n\nIf this sounds like fun, just get in touch by calling Irene directly at +34 650 049 726 or come by the restaurant. Registration and payment must be made no later than the Sunday before we play."
    },

    "eventOverlay": {
        "h3": "Events",
        "p": "Throughout the year we have a variety of different events, and some examples of events we hosted in previous years are shrimp evenings, Norwegian national dinner day (sheep and cabbage), May 17 (Norwegian national day) and Christmas Eve. For future events, just keep an eye on Facebook where all information about various events is updated. \n\nIf you have a special occasion to celebrate such as a birthday, wedding, or an occasion to gather a large group, just get in touch with us by phone +34 650 049 726 or come by in advance. We love to organize a great day for our guests."
    },

    "quizOverlay": {
        "h3": "Quiz",
        "p": "We organize Quiz every Tuesday at 20:00. Feel free to come by between 18-19:00 to get some food before we start. \n\nRegistration takes place when you arrive, right before we start and costs 3€ per person, all proceeds from the quiz go to charity."
    },

    "podcastPageTitle": "Podcast",

    "podcastText": "A podcast made by Norwegians for Norwegians. We talk about all sorts of information that might be nice to know about life here in Spain.",

